SUMMARY:ESENTIAI MM — Virtual Fixed Income Investor Call
DESCRIPTION:Reach out to your dealer to confirm timing and availability\n\n
 Virtual fixed income investor call coordinated by Citigroup. Specific time
  not provided\; assumed 10:00 AM ET start with 45-minute duration.\nIssuer
 : ESENTIA ENERGY DEVELOPMENT SAB DE CV (ESENTIAI MM)\n\nDeal context:\nEse
 ntia Energy Development SAB DE CV\, a Mexican energy company rated Baa3/BB
 B-/BBB- (investment grade) by Moody's\, S&P\, and Fitch respectively\, has
  mandated Bank of America\, Citigroup\, and ING as global coordinators and
  active joint bookrunners\, alongside Scotiabank and SMBC as active joint 
 bookrunners\, to arrange virtual fixed income investor calls beginning Mon
 day\, May 4\, 2026. The company is considering a dual-tranche USD-denomina
 ted benchmark-sized 144A/Reg S senior unsecured notes offering in 7-year a
 nd 12-year tenors\, subject to market conditions. No pricing guidance or d
 eal size has been specified at this mandate stage\, with Citigroup coordin
 ating logistics for the investor call process.
